abstract.label: Abstract
abstract.value: The videotapes in this collection, produced by the Office of Media Production, include promotional material, commencement footage and documentary footage of speakers, visitors and events. The tapes range in date from 1983-2007.

bioghist.head: History of the Office of Media Production

p.value: Guarino continues to run the department. Based on the project titles in the online finding aid, the collection contains promotional productions, University commencement ceremonies, lectures, panel discussions, and other events as well as B-roll footage of the NYU campus, study abroad sites and other New York City locations.

The videotapes in this collection include promotional material, news and documentary footage, as well as recordings of different speakers and events at NYU. The tapes comprise approximately 500 projects produced by the Office of Media Production.
